flowchart TD
    Keystroke[Keystroke event\npartial query prefix] --> Normalize[Normalize prefix\nlowercase, trim]
    Normalize --> TrieLookup[Prefix trie lookup\ntraverse to prefix node]
    TrieLookup --> Candidates[Retrieve top-K candidates\nby weight from trie]
    Candidates --> PersonalFilter[Apply personalization\nuser history, language, region]
    PersonalFilter --> TrendBoost[Apply trending boost\nfrom log processing]
    TrendBoost --> Rank[Rank completions\nby combined score]
    Rank --> SafetyFilter[Filter unsafe\nor low-quality suggestions]
    SafetyFilter --> Response[Return top 5-10 completions]
    Response --> UI[Render dropdown\nbelow search input]
    UI --> UserSelect{User selects\na completion?}
    UserSelect -->|Yes| SubmitQuery[Submit full query\nto search pipeline]
    UserSelect -->|No| Keystroke
